    <item>
      <title>LeetCode 295: Find Median from Data Stream</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/leetcode/heaps/median-from-data-stream/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/leetcode/heaps/median-from-data-stream/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h1&gt;🧩 LeetCode 295: Find Median from Data Stream ⭐ (Hard)&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Design a data structure that supports &lt;code&gt;addNum(int num)&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;findMedian()&lt;/code&gt; in $O(\log N)$ and $O(1)$ respectively.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;🎯 What the interviewer is testing&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;-what-the-interviewer-is-testing&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#-what-the-interviewer-is-testing&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Two-heap design pattern.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keeping heaps balanced (size difference ≤ 1).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lower half Max-Heap + Upper half Min-Heap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;🧠 Deep Explanation&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;-deep-explanation&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#-deep-explanation&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Design: Two Heaps&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;design-two-heaps&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#design-two-heaps&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;code&gt;smallHeap&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; (Max-Heap): stores the smaller half.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;code&gt;largeHeap&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; (Min-Heap): stores the larger half.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invariant: &lt;code&gt;smallHeap.size() == largeHeap.size()&lt;/code&gt; OR &lt;code&gt;smallHeap.size() == largeHeap.size() + 1&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;addNum:&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;addnum&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#addnum&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Always add to &lt;code&gt;smallHeap&lt;/code&gt; first.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rebalance: if &lt;code&gt;smallHeap.peek() &amp;gt; largeHeap.peek()&lt;/code&gt;, move top of small to large.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balance sizes: if &lt;code&gt;largeHeap.size() &amp;gt; smallHeap.size()&lt;/code&gt;, move top of large to small.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;findMedian:&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;findmedian&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#findmedian&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Odd total: return &lt;code&gt;smallHeap.peek()&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Even total: return average of both tops.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;✅ Ideal Answer&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;-ideal-answer&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#-ideal-answer&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;By partitioning the stream into two heaps—a max-heap for the lower half and a min-heap for the upper half—we can always access the median in $O(1)$ from the tops of the heaps. Rebalancing on each insertion is $O(\log N)$.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;💻 Java Code&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;-java-code&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#-java-code&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;
  

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;MedianFinder&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    PriorityQueue&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;Integer&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; small &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; PriorityQueue&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;(Collections.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;reverseOrder&lt;/span&gt;()); &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// max-heap&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    PriorityQueue&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;Integer&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; large &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; PriorityQueue&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;(); &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// min-heap&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;addNum&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; num) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        small.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;offer&lt;/span&gt;(num);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        large.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;offer&lt;/span&gt;(small.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;poll&lt;/span&gt;());
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (large.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;size&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; small.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;size&lt;/span&gt;()) small.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;offer&lt;/span&gt;(large.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;poll&lt;/span&gt;());
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;double&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;findMedian&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; small.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;size&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; large.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;size&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;?&lt;/span&gt; small.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;peek&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            : (small.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;peek&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; large.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;peek&lt;/span&gt;()) &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; 2.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

  
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;🔄 Follow-up Questions&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;-follow-up-questions&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#-follow-up-questions&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What if the stream is huge?&lt;/strong&gt; (Use reservoir sampling or quantile sketches like t-digest.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What if all numbers &amp;lt;= 100?&lt;/strong&gt; (Bucket sort / counting array approach — $O(1)$ add.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thread-safe version?&lt;/strong&gt; (Use &lt;code&gt;PriorityBlockingQueue&lt;/code&gt; with locks.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

      </description>
